translation[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,44,UMvelinqangi wenza ukuthi ubusuku nemini buguquguquke ngempela kuloko kunesifundo ebantwini ababonayo
  24,45,"Futhi uMvelinqangi wadala zonke izidalwa ezinyakazayo ngamanzi ezinye zazo yilezo ezikhasa ngezisu zazo futhi ezinye zazo yilezo ezihamba ngezinyawo ezimbili, ezinye zazo yilezo ezihamba ngezine. UMvelinqangi udala lokho akuthandayo, ngempela uMvelinqangi uyakwazi ukwenza zonke izinto"
  24,46,Ngempela sawembula amavesi acacile futhi uMvelinqangi uholela endleleni eqondile noma ngabe ngubani amthandayo
  24,47,"Futhi bathi, “sakholwa kuMvelinqangi nasesithunyweni futhi sahlonipha” ingxenye phakathi kwabo yabe seyiyafulathela emva kwalokho futhi labo abayibona abakholwayo"
  24,48,Futhi uma bemenyelwa kuMvelinqangi nasesithunyweni sakhe ukuze ehlulele phakathi kwabo bheka! Ingxenye yabo iphendukela emumva
  24,49,Uma iqiniso lingasohlangothini lwabo bazoza kuyena ngokuzinikela
  24,50,"Ngakube ezinhliziyweni zabo kunesifo na? Noma ngakube basekungabazeni yini na? Noma besaba ukuthi uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe bangase bangabi nobulungiswa kubona, Qha yibona uqobo abayizoni"
  24,51,"Kuphela okwakushiwo abakholwayo uma bemenyelwa kuMvelinqangi nasesithunyweni sakhe ukuze ehlulele phakathi kwabo ukuthi bathi, “sizwile futhi salalela futhi labo bayilabo abaphumelelayo”"
  24,52,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani ohlonipha uMvelinqangi nesithunywa sakhe futhi esaba uMvelinqangi futhi egwema okubi kuyena ngakho-ke labo bayilabo abaphumeleleyo
  24,53,"Futhi bafunga ngoMvelinqangi izifungo zabo ezinzima, bathi uma ubaphoqa bazophuma ithi, “musani ukufunga inhlonipho yenu iyaziwa ngempela uMvelinqangi wazi kabanzi ngalokho enikwenzayo”"